name: 1: Blue
description:
I saw a game somebody made up on r/quarantineactivities that read, “Pick a color. Find everything that is that color in your house and take a picture.” (Original post in my story)

I loved the idea and brought it to my partner, who responded with what I’d been thinking, “Why not do all of the colors of the rainbow?” So we wrote down all the colors on slips of paper, threw them in a hat, and picked our first color. 

Spoiler: it was blue.
